[TAE groaning]

502
00:21:04,567 --> 00:21:05,942
[SAKI]
So much for idol buzz.

503
00:21:06,025 --> 00:21:06,942
I guess so.

504
00:21:07,025 --> 00:21:09,317
[groaning]

505
00:21:09,400 --> 00:21:10,983
[HOST] Oops, I think she's
still got too much mud

506
00:21:11,067 --> 00:21:12,233
in her mouth to talk.

507
00:21:12,317 --> 00:21:14,858
Anyway, you were amazing!
Congratulations!

508
00:21:14,942 --> 00:21:17,775
Oh, well. What's done is done.

509
00:21:17,858 --> 00:21:18,900
[gasps]

510
00:21:20,192 --> 00:21:22,983
Hold on. Tae's
wearing two shirts.

511
00:21:23,067 --> 00:21:24,150
She is?

512
00:21:24,233 --> 00:21:26,942
Hey, take off
your outside shirt!

513
00:21:27,025 --> 00:21:27,942
[groaning]

514
00:21:28,025 --> 00:21:30,692
[grunting]

515
00:21:30,775 --> 00:21:31,733
[SAKURA]
Uh...

516
00:21:35,775 --> 00:21:38,067
[TAE crows]

517
00:21:38,150 --> 00:21:39,608
[CROWD cheering]

518
00:21:39,692 --> 00:21:42,150
[HOST]
Let's give her another hand!

519
00:21:42,233 --> 00:21:43,733
[SAKURA whines]

520
00:21:43,817 --> 00:21:46,108
[GIRLS]
♪ At Drive-In Tori! ♪

521
00:21:46,192 --> 00:21:47,317
Nice bird.

522
00:21:47,400 --> 00:21:50,400
[camera shutter clicking]

523
00:21:50,483 --> 00:21:53,442
They really are an adorable
bunch of girls, huh?

524
00:21:53,525 --> 00:21:56,692
Hey, wait a minute.
I remember now.

525
00:21:56,775 --> 00:21:58,233
[INUBASHI]
Remember what?

526
00:21:59,358 --> 00:22:01,442
[OKOBA]
I should look into this.

527
00:22:03,733 --> 00:22:09,692
<i>Moving on to a new path.</i>

528
00:22:09,775 --> 00:22:15,025
<i>My journey here has ended.</i>

529
00:22:15,108 --> 00:22:20,983
<i>But when I close my eyes,</i>

530
00:22:21,067 --> 00:22:26,358
<i>I'm overcome with memories.</i>

531
00:22:26,442 --> 00:22:29,317
<i>I don't care</i>

532
00:22:29,400 --> 00:22:32,442
<i>If we're apart</i>

533
00:22:32,525 --> 00:22:37,692
<i>I'll always feel you in my heart</i>

534
00:22:37,775 --> 00:22:40,192
<i>Your smile</i>

535
00:22:40,275 --> 00:22:43,900
<i>Sparkling with tears</i>

536
00:22:43,983 --> 00:22:52,358
<i>Forever in my mind</i>
<i>from year to year</i>

537
00:22:52,442 --> 00:22:58,358
<i>There's beauty to be</i>
<i>seen in this world</i>

538
00:22:58,442 --> 00:23:03,608
<i>I've seen kindness</i>
<i>heal the deepest wounds</i>

539
00:23:03,692 --> 00:23:09,275
<i>Our chapter has ended,</i>
<i>but we'll be alright.</i>

540
00:23:09,358 --> 00:23:15,275
<i>Keep your gaze ahead and</i>
<i>walk toward the light.</i>

541
00:23:15,358 --> 00:23:20,317
<i>Now it's time we say goodbye,</i>

542
00:23:20,400 --> 00:23:28,483
<i>but don't forget the memories.</i>

543
00:23:34,400 --> 00:23:35,733
[AI]
This is Ai.

544
00:23:35,817 --> 00:23:37,608
Whether it's clucking
like chickens or rolling in mud,

545
00:23:37,692 --> 00:23:40,733
we're doing whatever it takes
to get Saga's attention.

546
00:23:40,817 --> 00:23:43,567
Next time on
<i>ZOMBIE LAND SAGA</i> , Episode 6:

547
00:23:43,650 --> 00:23:46,650
"Because It's Sentimental SAGA."
Don't miss it.

